{
  "title": "Important WebSocket Change Notice — Base URL Split & Migration",
  "meta_description": "Background",
  "intro_blocks": [],
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Background",
      "level": 2,
      "id": "background",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Due to sustained heavy traffic, we have upgraded the WebSocket URL structure by introducing a root plus dedicated entry points for Public / Market / Private traffic. This separation improves stability, scalability, and operational isolation across different data types."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "What’s New",
      "level": 2,
      "id": "whats-new",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "3 new WebSocket base URLs (Root + routed paths) Public (high-frequency public market data): `wss://fstream.binance.com/public` Market (regular market data): `wss://fstream.binance.com/market` Private (user data): `wss://fstream.binance.com/private`",
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "list",
                  "ordered": false,
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "text": "Public (high-frequency public market data): `wss://fstream.binance.com/public`",
                      "blocks": []
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Market (regular market data): `wss://fstream.binance.com/market`",
                      "blocks": []
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Private (user data): `wss://fstream.binance.com/private`",
                      "blocks": []
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "Two access modes are supported `ws` mode: streams are composed in the URL path `stream` mode: streams are passed via query (e.g., `?streams=`) — private uses `listenKey/events`",
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "list",
                  "ordered": false,
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "text": "`ws` mode: streams are composed in the URL path",
                      "blocks": []
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "`stream` mode: streams are passed via query (e.g., `?streams=`) — private uses `listenKey/events`",
                      "blocks": []
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "Combined streams remain supported",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "Private supports listenKey + events subscription (multiple listenKeys and multiple events)",
              "blocks": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Examples",
      "level": 2,
      "id": "examples",
      "blocks": []
    },
    {
      "title": "Public / Market: combined subscriptions",
      "level": 3,
      "id": "public--market-combined-subscriptions",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "`ws` mode (path-based) `wss://fstream.binance.com/public/ws/bnbusdt@depth/ethusdt@depth` `wss://fstream.binance.com/market/ws/btcusdt@aggTrade/ethusdt@aggTrade`",
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "list",
                  "ordered": false,
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "text": "`wss://fstream.binance.com/public/ws/bnbusdt@depth/ethusdt@depth`",
                      "blocks": []
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "`wss://fstream.binance.com/market/ws/btcusdt@aggTrade/ethusdt@aggTrade`",
                      "blocks": []
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "`stream` mode (query-based) `wss://fstream.binance.com/market/stream?streams=bnbusdt@aggTrade/btcusdt@markPrice` `wss://fstream.binance.com/public/stream?streams=btcusdt@depth/ethusdt@depth`",
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "list",
                  "ordered": false,
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "text": "`wss://fstream.binance.com/market/stream?streams=bnbusdt@aggTrade/btcusdt@markPrice`",
                      "blocks": []
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "`wss://fstream.binance.com/public/stream?streams=btcusdt@depth/ethusdt@depth`",
                      "blocks": []
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Private: listenKey & events",
      "level": 3,
      "id": "private-listenkey--events",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "`ws` mode (listenKey + events) `wss://fstream.binance.com/private/ws?listenKey=<listenKey1>&events=ORDER_TRADE_UPDATE/ACCOUNT_UPDATE`",
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "list",
                  "ordered": false,
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "text": "`wss://fstream.binance.com/private/ws?listenKey=<listenKey1>&events=ORDER_TRADE_UPDATE/ACCOUNT_UPDATE`",
                      "blocks": []
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "`stream` mode (multiple listenKeys + events) `wss://fstream.binance.com/private/stream?listenKey=<listenKey1>&events=ORDER_TRADE_UPDATE&listenKey=<listenKey2>&events=ACCOUNT_UPDATE`",
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "list",
                  "ordered": false,
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "text": "`wss://fstream.binance.com/private/stream?listenKey=<listenKey1>&events=ORDER_TRADE_UPDATE&listenKey=<listenKey2>&events=ACCOUNT_UPDATE`",
                      "blocks": []
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "blockquote",
          "text": "JSON `SUBSCRIBE` is also supported; params may include market/public streams and listenKey event items."
        }
      ]
    },
